# The image needs only the prebuilt `quip-faucet` binary (staged at the repo
# root by CI / a local cargo build) and the entrypoint script. Ignore
# everything, then re-include just those. Top-level negations are reliable;
# negating a path inside an excluded dir (e.g. target/) is not.
*
!quip-faucet
!entrypoint.sh
